1
00:00:17,280 --> 00:00:18,200
What is that?

2
00:00:34,440 --> 00:00:35,600
Report!

3
00:00:35,800 --> 00:00:37,840
The Sea Clan army is invading!

4
00:00:45,440 --> 00:00:48,560
Li Jing!

5
00:00:58,560 --> 00:01:00,640
Archers, ready!

6
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,960
Draw bows!

7
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:11,800
Loose!

8
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:44,280
Oh no! It's trying to climb up!

9
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,160
Heavens!

10
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:56,240
How can this be?

11
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:58,440
Darn it!

12
00:01:58,440 --> 00:01:59,560
We can't hold them!

13
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:00,440
What do we do?

14
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:01,400
Darn it!

15
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,400
They're coming!

16
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:09,040
General!

17
00:02:09,040 --> 00:02:11,000
Can we still hold Chentang Pass?

18
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:18,760
Okay.

19
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:22,800
Welcome back to Tianjin Traffic Radio FM106.8.

20
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:25,320
It's another sunny day.

21
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:28,120
I hope your mood is as bright as today's weather.

22
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,400
Yu Han.

23
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:32,800
Did you see Er Tiao when you left for work?

24
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:34,120
I can't find him anywhere.

25
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,920
Where could a little bird go?

26
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:37,200
Hey, stop looking.

27
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,520
He flew to my office to find me again.

28
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:43,320
How many times have I told you not to run off?

29
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:44,280
You don't have a phone.

30
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:46,960
What if you got lost?

31
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,560
Look at you.

32
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:48,840
You act cute whenever I scold you.

33
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:49,920
Alright, alright.

34
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:50,840
Hurry home.

35
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:20,840
Where nine rivers meet the sea,

36
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,720
Chentang guards the coast.

37
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:24,280
We pray for a prosperous year,

38
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:27,480
with gentle rains and fair winds.

39
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:30,520
How did you get in here?
